Delivery Courier in the Philippines

Officially launched in 2019, J&T Express Philippines is a local courier service provider that is committed to providing express delivery services and international logistics as its core business. Known for its corporate excellence such as its mobile application, VIP platform, free door-to-door pickup, real-time order tracking system, affordable shipping, 24/7 customer service, and 365-day operations, all complemented by its nationwide delivery coverage.

OUR SERVICES

Standard Shipping (EZ)

We deliver your parcel the J&T Express way: receive packages hassle-free within 1-3 days depending on your location via land or sea.

Read More

International Shipping

Looking for international delivery services? Ship your packages fast and easy as J&T Express can be your international courier service provider with our international shipping service from the Philippines to Indonesia, Malaysia, Singapore, and Thailand.

Read More

Business Parcel (BP)

Ship parcels in the fastest way possible. Choose J&T Express as your courier service for fast shipping documents and packages through our Business Parcel (BP) delivery option which can be done via air shipping!

Read More

Plant Shipping

Certified plantitos and plantitas, rejoice! J&T Express is also your courier service partner for shipping plants nationwide.

Read More

VIP Account

From cash-on-delivery, express shipping, real-time tracking, and a VIP dashboard among other perks, experience an express delivery courier service like no other as our VIP client.

Read More

PROMOS

MAX SULIT SAYA PROMO

Introducing our Max Sulit Saya Promo. This promo applies to all pouch transactions nationwide. The shipping fee under the Max Sulit Saya Promo will be based on the "pouch size with a maximum weight limit". a maximum weight limit such as.. 3kg for Small (envelope) 3kg 5kg for Medium (A4) and 8kg for Large (A3)

PHP 21 VOUCHER

Affordable delivery services right at your fingertips. As part of our top-notch courier services, customers can avail the free PHP 21 voucher upon downloading the J&T Philippines mobile app.

J&T EXPRESS MOBILE APP

The J&T Express mobile application comes with the latest and exciting features that make your life easier. From real-time package monitoring to exciting deals and discounts, we got it all for you.
